<p><span class="caps">SSH</span> tip:</p>


	<p>If you run <span class="caps">SSH</span> on a non-standard port and can&#8217;t get the clone to work, put something like this in your ~/.ssh/config: http://p.caboo.se/118289</p>


	<p>Change hostname and port.</p>


	<p>Now all your other apps that use <span class="caps">SSH</span> on that server benefit too :)</p>
