<p>It &#8216;appears&#8217; based on the config presented in this article, that you are granting people ssh access to the git user (pubkey auth), while using /bin/sh (possibly aliased to bash) as the default shell.</p>


	<p>This would give any user added as a &#8216;git user&#8217; full shell access to that account.
