<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><span>Garry</span></span><span class="user-date"> on November 15, 2007 12:04 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>cactus,</p>


	<p>It does not give a full shell, because in ~/.ssh/authorized_keys we use &#8220;command=&#8221;</p>


	<p>This makes <span class="caps">SSH</span> execute only that command, you can&#8217;t get a login shell.</p>
</div>
