<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://eagain.net/">Tv</a></span><span class="user-date"> on November 15, 2007 12:11 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>I&#8217;ve fixed the caveats mentioned here, if someone in the audience had trouble, please try with the latest version.</p>


	<p>If you install gitosis outside of the usual <span class="caps">PYTHONPATH</span>, you will still need to add the containing directory to it, before running gitosis-init and for the incoming <span class="caps">SSH</span> sessions. This is a bit of a chicken-and-egg problem to try to solve within gitosis, so you should just make sure the environment is correct before gitosis is run. If anyone has a really neat solution for that, please let me know.</p>
</div>
<div class="add-comment-line"><!-- add line here --></div>
</div>

