<p>@lazz: if you are on ubuntu (or any debian flavor), you can enable the backport repositories for apt-get, then run &#8216;apt-get install git-core&#8217; or &#8216;sudo apt-get update &#38;&#38; sudo apt-get upgrade&#8217; and it will update git to 1.5.5.4.</p>


