<span class="user-postname"><span>solo</span></span><span class="user-date"> on May 01, 2008 07:17 AM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>Okay, got it.  My ~/git/.ssh/authorized_keys file already had the deployment user&#8217;s key before I added it with gitosis, and the two conflicted.  I removed the offending key, and git clone is happy now.</p>
