<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><span>anthony</span></span><span class="user-date"> on June 04, 2008 07:26 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>alessio: I have had this trouble, and it was created by an out-of-sync ssh public key. Solo&#8217;s comment above helped me out.</p>


	<p>There are three places the key is stored. Make sure that the key at &#8221;~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub&#8221; on your local computer (this is the original) is in agreement with the keys on the gitosis server:</p>


	<p>&#8221;/home/git/repositories/gitosis-admin.git/gitosis-export/keydir/<em>YourUsername</em>@<em>YourHostname</em>.pub&#8221; and in
&#8221;/home/git/.ssh/authorized_keys&#8221;</p>
</div>
<div class="add-comment-line"><!-- add line here --></div>
</div>

