<span class="user-postname"><span>FunnyMan</span></span><span class="user-date"> on October 13, 2008 07:27 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>The reason your custom port is failing is that git can&#8217;t figure out what you&#8217;re trying to do.  Use this form instead:</p>


	<p>ssh://git@myserver.com:1234/foo/bar</p>


	<p>Note the added protocol and the removed colon.</p>
</div>
