<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://blog.jasonmeridth.com">jmeridth</a></span><span class="user-date"> on February 26, 2009 09:26 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>1. I followed all the instructions
2. It worked great
3. Added new user.  Had bad pub key.  started everything over again.
4. I am able to work with gitosis-admin repo just fine
5. I have 2 other groups, one with the same user I use for gitosis-admin, and another of the newer user
6. group 2 has 8 repos</p>


	<p>[group userone]
members = userone@hostone
writable = one two three four five six seven eight</p>


