fatal: unable to connect a socket (Connection refused)</p>


	<pre><code>errno=Connection refused
errno=Connection refused</code></pre>


	<p>9. other group and user:</p>


	<p>[group usertwo]
members = usertwo@hosttwo
writable = one_repo</p>


