<p>mtkd: massive thanks! I hit exactly the same problem and was tearing my hair out trying to figure out why the first clone was faliing.</p>


	<p>garry: great article! its maybe worth updating the instructions to mention mtkd&#8217;s issue &#38; resolution; am sure others will hit this, needing to fix AlloowUsers etc.</p>


	<p>I found this page helped: https://help.ubuntu.com/8.04/serverguide/C/user-management.html</p>


	<p>I just hacked /etc/ssh/sshd_config and added &#8216;git&#8217; to AllowUsers and it then worked like a charm.</p>
