<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://www.webwarelab.com">punkrats</a></span><span class="user-date"> on April 21, 2009 10:13 AM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>Hi everyone,
I host several repositories with gitosis and had this error:</p>


	<p><span class="caps">ERROR</span>:gitosis.serve.main:Repository read access denied
fatal: The remote end hung up unexpectedly</p>


	<p>Solved it by assigning different groups in gitosis-admin/gitosis.conf, e.g.</p>


	<p>[group firstproject]
writable = firstproject
members = punkrats@Webware-Lab</p>


	<p>[group secondproject]
writable = secondproject
members = punkrats@Webware-Lab</p>


	<p>After commit and push origin master, everything worked as expected.
Cheers.</p>
</div>
<div class="add-comment-line"><!-- add line here --></div>
</div>

