<div class="user-text">
<p>Never mind &#8230; ignore previous question. It&#8217;s answered in the gitosis readme (/usr/share/doc/gitosis/README.Debian), and it&#8217;s clear that the &#8216;gitosis&#8217; user is meant to be the repository owner. Instructions should be updated to reflect this.</p>
