<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://snackycracky.wordpress.com">snackycracky</a></span><span class="user-date"> on June 26, 2009 02:04 AM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>the workaround for new repositories and the error
<b> fatal: free_monkey.git: unable to chdir or not a git archive fatal: The remote end hung up unexpectedly</b>
is to:</p>


	<p>mkdir ~/repositories/free_monkey.git
cd  ~/repositories/free_monkey.git &#38;&#38; git init&#8212;bare</p>
</div>
