<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://sunoano.name">Suno Ano</a></span><span class="user-date"> on July 24, 2009 06:39 AM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>Hi folks,</p>


	<p>about the issue with git-daemon-export-ok being automatically created &#8230; you have to use a [repo foo] stanza and not a [group foo] stanza; see here
http://sunoano.name/ws/public_xhtml/scm.html#providing_a_repository_to_the_world for more info</p>
</div>
