<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><span>Tim</span></span><span class="user-date"> on July 25, 2009 09:33 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>To those of you having the &#8220;read access denied&#8221; error when trying to do your initial push to the repository:  Make sure you ran the &#8216;chmod&#8217; command in the tutorial.  That was the only thing I skipped, and was having the mentioned problem.  It appears that the config file doesn&#8217;t get updated with your new repository settings if you skip that step.</p>
</div>
<div class="add-comment-line"><!-- add line here --></div>
