<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://t6d.com">Theo</a></span><span class="user-date"> on August 31, 2009 09:22 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>Just a note to others about permissions on the authorized_keys file; I had to make the following permission changes before gitosis would update this file:</p>


	<p>chmod 755 /home/git
chmod 700 /home/git/.ssh
chmod 644 /home/git/.ssh/authorized_keys</p>


	<p>Prior to these changes git kept asking for a password for users who I had added to the keydir but were not been persisted to authorized_keys. Obviously there are security implications to these changes.</p>
</div>
<div class="add-comment-line"><!-- add line here --></div>
</div>

