<p>I was still getting the <span class="caps">ERROR</span>:gitosis.serve.main:Repository read access denied problem after rechecking everything that was said here. I finally found the answer on stackoverflow. Make sure your repositories/gitosis-admin.git/hooks/post-update is executable. Enjoy.</p>
