<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://techdebug.com">Lantrix</a></span><span class="user-date"> on January 06, 2010 06:46 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
How I installed python setup-tools, then gitosis, on OpenBSD 4.5
<code>
sudo pkg_add -v python-2.5.4
sudo ln -sf /usr/local/bin/python2.5 /usr/local/bin/python
sudo ln -sf /usr/local/bin/python2.5-config /usr/local/bin/python-config
sudo ln -sf /usr/local/bin/pydoc2.5 /usr/local/bin/pydoc
sudo pkg_add -v py-setuptools
git clone git://eagain.net/gitosis
cd gitosis
python setup.py install
</code>
</div>
