<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://justinlilly.com">Justin Lilly</a></span><span class="user-date"> on January 23, 2010 09:39 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>I was getting the error</p>


	<pre><code>ERROR:gitosis.serve.main:Repository read access denied fatal: The remote end hung up unexpectedly</code></pre>


	<p>which was due to my post-update hook not being fired. If this happens, su into your git user, then try to run the hook manually. I got some complaints regarding <span class="caps">GIT</span>_DIR. To fix this, I added</p>


	<pre><code>GIT_DIR=$HOME/repositories/gitosis-admin.git/</code></pre>


	<p>to my git user&#8217;s .bashrc which solved it.</p>
</div>
