<p>With regard the post above: I spent almost 6 hours on this and a hero named Ilari on irc://irc.freenode.net/git solved it in 30 seconds.  The key is that gitosis-init works only once.  I wish that the manual had pointed that out.  The hero recommended that I check out Gitolite.  Thank you !</p>
