<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://jonsview.com">jmstacey</a></span><span class="user-date"> on March 03, 2010 01:38 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>On Mac <span class="caps">OS X</span> Server 10.6 (Snow Leopard) if you encounter an error such as remote end hung up unexpectedly make sure that the git account can find the gitosis-serve binary. This might require modifying the git user&#8217;s .bashrc file with the proper path. Also, don&#8217;t forget to give the git account remote login capabilities through system preferences.</p>
</div>
