<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><span>peter</span></span><span class="user-date"> on June 09, 2010 10:03 AM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>I was also in touch with</p>


	<p>&#8220;Repository read access denied&#8221;</p>


	<p>and in my case the error was thrown because the right key wasn&#8217;t in the ssh-keychain. you can check this with ssh-add -l. if necessary you can add the right key with ssh-add /root/.ssh/&lt;keyfile&gt;.</p>


	<p>regards from germany,
peter</p>
