<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><span>gdw</span></span><span class="user-date"> on July 12, 2010 02:48 PM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>I was getting:</p>


	<p><span class="caps">ERROR</span>:gitosis.serve.main:Repository read access denied</p>


	<p>It seemed to be happening because I had a repo in my gitosis.conf that didn&#8217;t exist.  I hope this helps someone.  I removed the &#8216;writable&#8217; line, and it worked.</p>


	<p>Gitosis, <span class="caps">IMO</span>, is too flakey, but I don&#8217;t know if there&#8217;s anything better.</p>
</div>
