<div class="user-text">
<p>I fat-fingered the adduser command, and the shell ended up being /bin/sh/. That extra slash at the end was causing some issues. Took a while to figure out ( had to edit /etc/passwd manually ), but once I had it figured out it was a quick fix.</p>
