<div id="comments-box"> 
<span class="user-postname"><a href="http://puritea.weebly.com/">Puritea</a></span><span class="user-date"> on November 30, 2010 04:09 AM</span>
<div class="user-text">
<p>Peter, if your /etc/ssh/sshd_config file has UsePAM yes, then <span class="caps">PAM</span> may have denied you logging in as your git user because of various reasons. The most common one Ive seen is that the account is locked. What makes an account locked is dependent on your <span class="caps">PAM</span> setup. Changing the password field for the git user in /etc/shadow from ! to a * has been reported to solve the problem.</p>


	<p><a href="http://puritea.weebly.com/">Puritea</a></p>
</div>
<div class="add-comment-line"><!-- add line here --></div>
